title: Proposal for Adjustments to Farm Rewards
body:
As mentioned in a [**tweet earlier today** ](https://twitter.com/PancakeSwap/status/1421412567675596812?s=20), this is the biggest adjustment proposal yet, and while also fulfilling the usual goal of re-directing liquidity to key/high value farms from low liquidity/low volume farms, it will also us to follow up with a proposal for a bigger reduction to emissions without affecting key/high value farms.

I would once again like to reiterate that fact that rewards aren't removed during ajustments, they are just distributed back across all other existing farms, in addition to giving us more space to add more new Syrup Pool/farm combos etc.

For more information on how adjustments are cayou can check out a previous proposal -
[**CLICK TO READ**](https://pancakeswap.finance/voting/proposal/QmU8itX17Jm8hhwWRhvaWUCnz2CxZkBri8Ey6xvVotf5Qh)

**TLDR:**

- Farms to be discontinued = **36**
- Farms to have weight lowered = **20**
- Farms to have weight increased = **2**
- **Total Weight returned to existing farms = 17.9**
